C}} [[Marvin Rodr\u00edguez]]||1999\u201300\n|-\n|{{flagicon|BRA}} [[G\u00edlson Nunes]]||2000\n|-\n|{{flagicon|CRC}} [[Alexandre Guimar\u00e3es]]||2001\u201302\n|-\n|{{flagicon|CRC}} [[Rodrigo Kenton]]||2002*\n|-\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Steve Sampson]]||2003\u201304\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Colombia}} [[Jorge Luis Pinto]]||2004\u201305\n|-\n|{{flagicon|CRC}} [[Alexandre Guimar\u00e3es]]||2005\u201306\n|-\n|{{flagicon|CRC}} [[Carlos Watson (footballer)|Carlos Watson]]||2006*\n|-\n|{{flagicon|CRC}} [[Hern\u00e1n Medford]]||2007\u201308\n|-\n|{{flagicon|CRC}} [[Rodrigo Kenton]]||2008\u201309\n|-\n|{{flagicon|BRA}} [[Ren\u00ea Sim\u00f5es]]||2009\n|-\n|{{flagicon|CRC}} [[R\u00f3nald Gonz\u00e1lez Brenes]]||2010*\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Colombia}} [[Jorge Luis Pinto]]||2011\u20132014\n|-\n|{{flagicon|CRC}} [[Paulo Wanchope]]|| 2014\u20132015\n|-\n|{{flagicon|CRC}} [[\u00d3scar Ram\u00edrez (footballer)|\u00d3scar Ram\u00edrez]]|| 2015\u20132018\n|-\n|{{flagicon|CRC}} [[R\u00f3nald Gonz\u00e1lez Brenes]] (Interim)|| 2018\n|-\n|{{flagicon|URU}} [[Gustavo Matosas]] || 2018\u20132019\n|-\n|{{flagicon|CRC}} [[Douglas Sequeira]] (Interim) || 2019\n|-\n|{{flagicon|CRC}} [[Ronald Gonzalez Brenes]] || 2019-\n|-\n|}\n|}\n</div>\n\n===Coaching staff===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: left\"\n|-\n!Position\n!Name\n|-\n|Manager || [[R\u00f3nald Gonz\u00e1lez Brenes]]\n|-\n|Assistant Coach 1|| [[Douglas Sequeira]]\n|-\n|Assistant Coach 2|| [[Mauricio Solis]]\n|-\n|Goalkeeper's Coach || [[Luis Gabelo Conejo]]\n|-\n|Youth Co-ordinator || [[Luis Roberto Sibaja]]\n|-\n|Medical Director   || [[Dr. Alejandro Ramirez]]\n|-\n|}\n\n===Record versus other nations===\n: ''As of 2011-03-25''\n\n{|class=\"sortable wikitable collapsible collapsed\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:250px;\"| Nation\n! style=\"width:50px;\"| Pld\n! style=\"width:50px;\"| W\n! style=\"width:50px;\"| D\n! style=\"width:50px;\"| L\n! style=\"width:50px;\"| GF\n! style=\"width:50px;\"| GA\n! style=\"width:50px;\"| GD\n! style=\"width:50p